Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,460)}Jednou pojedu v kánoi na červeném koberci.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,464)}Je to Cannes,
